text:
Given that the Ohio State football team admittedly has underperformed numerous times this season, one has to wonder about the priorities of its fan base when the No.1 topic this past week wasn't the players in the opposing uniforms tonight in Ohio Stadium but rather the uniforms that will be on the Buckeyes.
Nevertheless, OSU will be clad in black when it faces Penn State under the lights in what is being promoted as "Dark Night in the Shoe" by the university. What shade of dark remains to be seen.
