Whether you're at the game or watching on TV, a perfect complement to your game-day experience is following The Dispatch's Rob Oller for Scarlet and Gray Matter on Twitter .
For the past decade Oller has been entertaining Dispatch readers with his SGM columns on Sundays following OSU football games. Now you can receive SGM nuggets during the action. Rob can be found on Twitter at @rollerCD .
